        {
            "title": "午後偏軟 滬指收跌3點 深指跌0.85% 芯片相關股捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地A股午後窄幅偏軟，滬深兩市交投增至約3.25萬億元(人民幣‧下同)，金礦與石油股持續強勢，芯片與半導體相關股則捱沽，天岳先進(02631)A股(688234.SH)挫逾9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：天岳先進科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250225_FI_source-web_SICC-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：天岳先進科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250225_FI_source-web_SICC-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：天岳先進科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早高開8點後略為反覆，於早市中段最高曾報4160點，升24點，在不足半小時內便跌至全日低位4124點，跌11點，其後進入好淡爭持局面，午市一直在升或跌10點以內上落；滬指最後收報4132點，轉跌3點或0.09%，成交1.45萬億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指高開低走，今早高開52點後於初段升幅曾擴大至93點，衝上14532點便暫時無以為繼，開市不足15分鐘便轉跌直至收市，午後最低曾報14277點，跌161點，但午市波幅卻不足100點；深指收報14316點，跌123點或0.85%，成交1.8億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數則升4點或0.1%，以4706點收市；創業板指數跌30點或0.91%，報3319點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">芯片及半導體相關股跌多升少，第3代半導體碳半矽襯底生產商天岳先進A、H齊挫，A股收跌9.5%，報101.27元；峰岹科技(01304)A股(688279.SH)跌6.11%，報207元；納芯微(02676)A股(688052.SH)跌5.82%，報179.3元；復旦微電(01385)A股(688385.SH)跌5.25%，報81.38元；豪威(00501)A股(603501.SH)則跌3.69%，報124.62元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AI芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)跌2.62%，報1300元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)亦跌2.43%，報121.92元。不過，華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)卻突圍升2.21%，報142.85元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價創新高，金礦股再度炒上。赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)升幅擴大至9.97%，報42.69元；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升9.94%，報55.74元；紫金(02899)A股(601899.SH)升幅則略為收窄至5.17%，報39.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「三桶油」持續強勢，中國海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)漲6.66%，報33.49元；中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)升5.7%，報10.39元；中國石化(00386)A股(600028.SH)也升3.74%，報6.38元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15612783-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c3%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c0-85-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e8%82%a1%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp",
